Pukapu heard the story from
the Avaritia Trade Guild, mo.

rows.label: qst103911_msg0002
rows.name:
Pukapu will sell friends a
long-distance Divine Beast ship, mo!

rows.label: qst103911_msg0009
rows.name:
The ship costs 300,000G, and the
mooring fee is 500G... so the
total comes to 300,500G, mo.

rows.label: qst103911_msg0003
rows.name:
With this, you are now a ship
owner, mo! Congratulations, mo!

rows.label: qst103911_msg0004
rows.name:
Pukapu will handle the registration
with the Avaritia Trade Guild, mo.

rows.label: qst103911_msg0005
rows.name:
Pukapu wishes you a safe
journey, mo. Bye-bye, mo~!

rows.label: qst103911_msg0010
rows.name:
This is a big purchase, so
Pukapu understands if friends
need to think, mo.
